text: George Alfred O'Connor (28 March 1892 – 23 September 1921) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Richmond and St Kilda in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:1892 births Category:1921 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Richmond Football Club players Category:St Kilda Football Club players
